{"tid":1987334,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有女無啦啦撩我男朋友傾計","createTime":"2020-04-24T11:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T20:39:07.000Z","uid":200587,"like":95,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4304bb471c5b45e1bc431dd92203077a1b0efccf","tid":1987334,"uid":200587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"佢哋郵寄啲yell card俾對方<br />\n最初問下對方收到未呀嗰啲<br />\n然後條女無啦啦同我男朋友講佢公司啲嘢 <br />\n係到吐苦水<br />\n佢哋尋晚已經開始傾<br />\n但我男朋友冇同我講因為我尋晚發脾氣<br />\n佢話如果佢再講 我會再嬲<br />\n今日接佢放工 瞄左佢電話一眼先知有呢條女存在<br />\n佢同我講 放心喎 冇人想溝你男朋友<br />\n<br />\n咁其實我應唔應該嬲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外一問如果我繼續俾佢地傾 會唔會好蠢..<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔嬲"},{"pid":"1f14a78432cd5e70166433bba52ed92a57df8114","tid":1987334,"uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"搵定下一個啦"},{"pid":"9dde6c839454c0ae275b0017db2e89f255d1ed6e","tid":1987334,"uid":3852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"mola mola"},{"pid":"c4b7ec40c42ece5315c84efdb165beb10003e89d","tid":1987334,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"你綠了"},{"pid":"81dbb55495c969f66808d7c2a9b0a73ab173dc4d","tid":1987334,"uid":69289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:48:47.000Z","msg":"河童滑石 ... GAY <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0fbe1d703d0a92cca8a5f4d8ac74bc18069400","tid":1987334,"uid":50888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"放心喎 冇人想溝你男朋友"},{"pid":"1e8320217c75e4c8423088310d2ca27108bcf066","tid":1987334,"uid":82310,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:50:0